    <abstract>
      <t>   This specification defines a means of computing a thumbprint value
   (a.k.a. digest) of JSON Web Key (JWK) objects analogous to the "x5t"
   (X.509 Certificate SHA-1 Thumbprint) value defined for X.509
   certificate objects.

	 </t>
